# Game Architecture

## Composition Root

`SkirmishDirector` (`[DefaultExecutionOrder(-50)]`) is the **composition root**. It runs first and:
1. Reads `GameSession` for difficulty and selected map (`SkirmishMapDefinition`)
2. Builds the world (terrain, clay, hives, fruit nodes, terrain features, passive scatter)
3. Bakes the **NavMesh** at runtime
4. Spawns starting units for both teams via `SpawnUnit()`
5. Creates a `Systems` GameObject and adds all runtime services as components:
   `PlayerResources`, `SelectionController`, `CommandController`, `GameHUD`, `Sc2BottomBar`,
   `SkirmishMinimap`, `FogOfWarSystem`, `MatchDirector`, `EnemyCommander`, `PauseController`, `GameAudio`

## Core Systems Map

```
SkirmishDirector (bootstrap)
├── Economy
│   ├── PlayerResources (singleton, Calories, events)
│   ├── EnemyResources (static mirror for AI)
│   ├── RottingFruitNode (harvestable, registered in RtsSimRegistry)
│   └── HiveDeposit (PlayerHive / EnemyHive statics, deposit + worker production)
├── Units
│   ├── InsectUnit (orders state machine, combat, gather, patrol)
│   ├── UnitDefinition (ScriptableObject — stats per archetype)
│   ├── RtsSimRegistry (static registry — fast iteration, no FindObjectsByType)
│   └── WorkerInventory (cargo tracking for workers)
├── Production
│   ├── ProductionBuilding (queue, costs, spawn, rally; types: Underground, AntNest, SkyTower)
│   ├── NestEvolution (one-time player upgrade)
│   └── BuildZoneRegistry (placement rings around hives/fruit)
├── Player Interaction
│   ├── SelectionController (click, box-select, double-click same-type)
│   ├── CommandController (right-click orders, building placement, pending commands)
│   ├── Sc2BottomBar (StarCraft-style HUD: minimap, selection, command grid)
│   └── RTSCameraController (pan, zoom, minimap click)
├── AI
│   ├── EnemyCommander (macro: build, produce, attack waves, defend)
│   └── SimpleEnemyAi (per-unit micro: gather, aggro, kite, flee; implements IAiController)
├── Vision
│   ├── FogOfWarSystem (256² texture, R=explored, G=current; disables enemy renderers)
│   └── TerrainFeatureRegistry (vision blocking, speed/concealment zones)
├── Match Flow
│   ├── MatchDirector (win/lose by alive count, overlay, Time.timeScale)
│   └── PauseController
└── Cross-Scene
    ├── GameSession (static — difficulty, selected map, PlayerPrefs keys)
    └── SceneLoader (Home → Game; SkirmishDemo is dev-only)
```

## Unit Archetypes

No deep class hierarchy — all units are `InsectUnit` + `UnitDefinition`. Archetype enum drives behavior:
- **Worker** — gathers calories, builds, cheap; UI name "Worker"
- **BasicFighter** — melee combat; UI name "Mantis"
- **BasicRanged** — cone spray attack (`SprayAttack`); UI name "Beetle" / "Bombardier"

## Important Statics and Singletons

| Type | Access Pattern | Purpose |
|------|---------------|---------|
| `SelectionController.Instance` | Singleton | Current selection state |
| `PlayerResources.Instance` | Singleton | Player economy + `OnCaloriesChanged` event |
| `FogOfWarSystem.Instance` | Singleton | Fog queries and texture |
| `GameAudio.Instance` | Singleton | Sound effects |
| `Sc2BottomBar.Instance` | Singleton | Bottom bar UI |
| `HiveDeposit.PlayerHive/EnemyHive` | Static refs | Main nests |
| `EnemyResources` | Static class | AI economy |
| `RtsSimRegistry` | Static class | Unit and fruit node registry |
| `ProductionBuilding.All` | Static list | All production buildings |
| `GameSession` | Static class | Cross-scene state |

## Communication Patterns

- **C# events** for economy UI: `PlayerResources.OnCaloriesChanged`
- **Direct references** and **static registries** — no event bus or messaging framework
- **Singletons** set in `Awake`/`OnEnable`, cleared in `OnDestroy`/`OnDisable`
- **Registry pattern**: units call `RtsSimRegistry.Register/Unregister` in `OnEnable/OnDisable`

## Difficulty Scaling

`GameSession.Difficulty` (`DemoDifficulty` enum) scales: enemy HP multiplier, AI think interval, opening unit counts, starting calories.
